description: This top 10% Cooter purrs with a rating of 87, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 174, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [174 Votes, Top 10%]
